    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3728",
      "text": "from [桶地下]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3729",
      "text": "桶地下攻略2026-02-17~(ネタバレ注意)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f372a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f372b",
      "text": "2026-02-17",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f372c",
      "text": "新情報公開予定",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f372d",
      "text": "\tシステムトラブルみたい[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f372e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f372f",
      "text": "22:12[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3730",
      "text": " [~ アングラサイトは更新なし、桶地下考に更新あり、祭りの名前を入れた先にページが増えている。]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3731",
      "text": "\tこの謎は自力で解いてないので進むかどうか迷うんだけどね、気になるから進んじゃう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3732",
      "text": "\t\t[~ さらにいくつかの問いが発生している]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3733",
      "text": "\t\t\t[~ 名物料理、これはアングラサイトの解読で分かった]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3734",
      "text": "\t\t\tわからない謎が3つある: [~ 桶地下で行われているとみられる祭りの「掛け声」、閉店したはずの店の名前、桶地下で行われている儀式の正式名称]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3735",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3736",
      "text": "23:54[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3737",
      "text": "\t水の効果で1日2問謎解きを獲得する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3738",
      "text": "\t\t謎解きを答えて正解！の画面に地下文字がある！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3739",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f373a",
      "text": "2026/2/18",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f373b",
      "text": "\t今回のゲームのメカニズムが機能してない可能性が出てきたw[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f373c",
      "text": "\t>[nishio https://x.com/nishio/status/2023772626829574615] #100謎コースター 22秒前に投稿されたものをクリックしても問題が増えないので問題シェア機能が単純に機能不全なのではという気がしてきた(初日いきなりシステム障害起きてたしな...)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f373d",
      "text": " > それともシェアされた問題の獲得方法が間違ってる？どうしたらいいの？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f373e",
      "text": " >[nishio https://x.com/nishio/status/2023774632353165343] 自分視点では`ttps://www.pub-riddle.com/share/?qid=1-29&guid=TxxHVps6D635vJIQ8E1n61ELq`というようにIDが積まれたリンクになっているが、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f373f",
      "text": " > 他人の投稿を見るとトップページへのリンクになっているように見えて、実際それをクリックしてもトップページの企画解説にしかいかない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3740",
      "text": " > [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HBXj8dxbcAEEHq_?format=jpg&name=small#.png] [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HBXkDTYbcAMzCeX?format=jpg&name=900x900#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3741",
      "text": " >[nishio https://x.com/nishio/status/2023928728804569446] 寝て起きたら謎が解けたかも知れないんだが、謎共有リンクが「ログインしていなければトップページへリダイレクト」という挙動であることによってXのクローラがOGP作成のために訪問したタイミングでリダイレクトされ、X側はそれを検知してリンク先をリダイレクト後のURLにするのでは #100謎コースター",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3742",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3743",
      "text": "謎が解けたw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3744",
      "text": "https://x.com/hanataro_kp/status/2023964010916495828?s=46&t=gkSZtjGEtUZPO0JCzBxCBw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3745",
      "text": "見た目の似ている2つの投稿が同じハッシュタグで行われており、それを見分ける必要があったようだ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3746",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3747",
      "text": "謎を獲得するリンク",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3748",
      "text": "https://search.yahoo.co.jp/realtime/search?ei=UTF-8&md=t&p=%23mcc_class1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3749",
      "text": " 有益情報だ、ありがたい[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f374a",
      "text": "　受け取り期限は1時間、20時に新しいものが配布される[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f374b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f374c",
      "text": "20:00",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f374d",
      "text": " すごい！無限に謎解きが来る！！[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f374e",
      "text": "　　14,20,21以外集まった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f374f",
      "text": "\t\t\t21以外集まった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3750",
      "text": "\t\t\thttps://search.yahoo.co.jp/realtime/search?p=%23mcc_class1+q21&ei=UTF-8&ifr=tl_sc",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3751",
      "text": "\t\t\t番号で検索",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3752",
      "text": "\t16番難しかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3753",
      "text": "\tq26で`丙`が出た",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3754",
      "text": "\tp36もとってなかった！とり損ねた！ https://search.yahoo.co.jp/realtime/search?p=%23mcc_class1+q36&ei=UTF-8&ifr=tl_sc",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3755",
      "text": "\t\tとれた！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3756",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83e7",
      "text": "from [2026/02/17]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659303,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83e8",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659308
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83ea",
      "text": " 昨日claudeと一緒に謎解きしてて、claudeがなんか考えてる時に人間は飽きてぶらぶらしてたらたまたま桶文字の法則っぽいものを見つけ、うれしくてclaudeに見つけたっぽい！て言ったら「うそ！ほんとじゃーんすご！」みたいに一緒に喜んでくれて楽しかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83eb",
      "text": "  AI時代の人間の役割、これかも",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83ec",
      "text": "  まだ途中すぎて7割くらいしか確定じゃないのでもう少しやる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83ed",
      "text": "   あれから進めて8-9割くらいになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83ee",
      "text": "\t\t「桶文字の法則」気になる[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83ef",
      "text": "\t\t いいかんじのヒントだしたい[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83f0",
      "text": "\t\t [~ 検索のページが結構重要で、このページがあるおかげで技術にあまり詳しくない人も解けるようになっている]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999604300000000003b83f5",
      "text": "\t\t \t[~ ソフトウェアキーボードでへんとつくりが明示されているのは良いよね][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659332,
      "updated": 1771659366
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83f1",
      "text": "\t\t[桶地下#698e1f190000000000189386][- できた〜🙌]できたと思ったけどちがってた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83f2",
      "text": "\t\t [ええー？ほんとにござるかぁ？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83f3",
      "text": "\t\t たしかにほんとでござった、余の早とちりであった、あいすまぬ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659304
    },
    {
      "id": "6999602700000000003b83f4",
      "text": "\t\t\t切り出したらリンク先どこかわからなくなっちゃったごめん[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659304,
      "updated": 1771659389
    },
    {
      "id": "69995da400000000006f3757",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658661,
      "updated": 1771658661
    },
    {
      "id": "699960a400000000003b8414",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659429,
      "updated": 1771659429
    },
    {
      "id": "6999608900000000003b83f6",
      "text": "from [2026/02/18]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659402,
      "updated": 1771659402
    },
    {
      "id": "6999608a00000000003b83f7",
      "text": "桶地下進捗:昨夜はわかったと思ったなんとか本祭が全然解けてなかったので、仕方なく新しいツールを作ってたら夜中になってしまい眠かった[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659402,
      "updated": 1771659405
    },
    {
      "id": "6999608a00000000003b83f9",
      "text": " 可能性がありすぎる〜",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659402,
      "updated": 1771659402
    },
    {
      "id": "6999608a00000000003b83fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659402,
      "updated": 1771659402
    },
    {
      "id": "699960a300000000003b8413",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659428,
      "updated": 1771659428
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609c00000000003b83fb",
      "text": "from [2026/02/19]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659421,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b83fd",
      "text": "桶地下攻略2026-02-17~(ネタバレ注意)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b83fe",
      "text": " [100謎コースター]のクロスワード、claude opusに丸投げしたらほぼひとりで解いた[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b83ff",
      "text": "  すごい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8400",
      "text": "  \tすごい[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8401",
      "text": "  \t\t僕は1日イベントで不在だったので全然解けてない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8402",
      "text": "  最後の当てはめるとこだけもったいないので人間が解いた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8403",
      "text": "  ヒントは75%くらいそろった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8404",
      "text": "  34番の謎がどうしてもわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8405",
      "text": "  \t解けてない: 17, 32, 34, 36、入手してない: 21[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8406",
      "text": "  \t07,21,27,31,35,36が未入手[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8407",
      "text": "  \t\t全部入手できた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8408",
      "text": "  ちなみに時間帯のリミットを使い切り、3ドル分くらいはみ出てたw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8409",
      "text": "   まあ裏でsonnetくんも別タスクやってたから…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b840a",
      "text": "  途中で何回か止まって、続きを促したりした。おそらく考え中の時のトークン数に制限があり、超えると止まっちゃうのだと思う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "699960ac00000000003b8415",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659436,
      "updated": 1771659436
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b840b",
      "text": " [桶地下]やる時間が取れてないので取って追いつきたい[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659436
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b840f",
      "text": "  [100謎コースター]でwebに出現しない文字がたくさん出ているので共有分を取るだけ取っておくといいかも[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8410",
      "text": "\t\t昨日20:00からの1時間くらいでほぼ全部取れたから、バランス調整は正しかったのだろうか？となってるw[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8411",
      "text": "  何か知らない情報がたくさんあるw[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609d00000000003b8412",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659422,
      "updated": 1771659422
    },
    {
      "id": "6999609c00000000003b83fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771659421,
      "updated": 1771659421
    },
    {
      "id": "69995e2e00000000008b2f0f",
      "text": "from [2026/02/20]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658798,
      "updated": 1771658798
    },
    {
      "id": "69995e2e00000000008b2f10",
      "text": "桶地下攻略2026-02-17~(ネタバレ注意)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658798,
      "updated": 1771658798
    },
    {
      "id": "69995e2e00000000008b2f11",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658798,
      "updated": 1771658798
    },
    {
      "id": "69995e2e00000000008b2f12",
      "text": " [100謎コースター]の34、1日半考えてわからなかったので公式Discordでヒント探して見てから考えたら30秒でわかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658798,
      "updated": 1771658798
    },
    {
      "id": "69995e2e00000000008b2f13",
      "text": "  コンプリートした！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658798,
      "updated": 1771658798
    },
    {
      "id": "69995e2e00000000008b2f14",
      "text": "  追い越された！[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658798,
      "updated": 1771658798
    },
    {
      "id": "69995e2e00000000008b2f15",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658798,
      "updated": 1771658798
    },
    {
      "id": "69995e2e00000000008b2f16",
      "text": "2026/2/21",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771658798,
      "updated": 1771674406
    },
    {
      "id": "69999b260000000000f5fefa",
      "text": "\tできた！[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771674407,
      "updated": 1771674409
    },
    {
      "id": "69999b270000000000f5fefb",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/d0d547b42ade8de65a3b0cbaab274721]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771674407,
      "updated": 1771674407
    },
    {
      "id": "69999b260000000000f5fef9",
      "text": "\t\t[~ そういえば各問題の下に書いてあるヒントって何だ？と気になって全部書き出してみた結果「マジかよ、2つのクロスワードの出現文字分布が共通なのかよ」となった。3問くらい解けてないけど既出の文字を塗りつぶしていってそれをヒントに「うばたま」と「きい」を埋めて回答]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771674406,
      "updated": 1771674564
    },
    {
      "id": "69999b2b0000000000f5fefc",
      "text": "\t\tq17, q32, q36は解けてない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771674411,
      "updated": 1771674609
    },
    {
      "id": "69999be90000000000f5fefe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771674602,
      "updated": 1771674602
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51c4a0000000000637075",
      "text": "桶地下攻略2026-03-09~(ネタバレ注意)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774525515,
      "updated": 1774525523
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51c570000000000637076",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774525528,
      "updated": 1774525528
    },
    {
      "id": "69aeb0e10000000000e41b5e",
      "text": " 3/9 class2はじまった！[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773056225,
      "updated": 1773056259
    },
    {
      "id": "69aeb1040000000000e41b60",
      "text": " https://search.yahoo.co.jp/realtime/search?p=%23mcc_class2&aq=-1&ei=UTF-8&ifr=tl_sc",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773056260,
      "updated": 1773056264
    },
    {
      "id": "69aeb0e20000000000e41b5f",
      "text": "  謎取得用",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773056227,
      "updated": 1773056377
    },
    {
      "id": "69aeb17c0000000000e41b62",
      "text": " 1個もわからない、仕組みをそもそも理解してない感じある[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773056381,
      "updated": 1773056412
    },
    {
      "id": "69aeb16d0000000000e41b61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773056366,
      "updated": 1773056366
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51a78000000000063706f",
      "text": "2026/3/26",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774525048,
      "updated": 1774525049
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51a7a0000000000637071",
      "text": "\tよいしょ[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774525050,
      "updated": 1774525052
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51cfb0000000000637077",
      "text": " \t色々忙しくて放置してた桶地下のことを久しぶりに見た",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774525691,
      "updated": 1774525694
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51cfc0000000000637078",
      "text": " \t\tClass2の謎を取得しようかと思ったけどもう全部持ってた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774525692,
      "updated": 1774525707
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51b6e0000000000637074",
      "text": "\t\tこれは... Class1の謎を使うのか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774525294,
      "updated": 1774525303
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51acb0000000000637073",
      "text": "\t\t全然わからん",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774525132,
      "updated": 1774525683
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51a790000000000637070",
      "text": "\tこれは1問だけ見ても解けないのではないか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774525049,
      "updated": 1774526359
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51f97000000000063707b",
      "text": "\t\t[~ Q09とQ26]に共通のパターンがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774526360,
      "updated": 1774526395
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51fb3000000000063707c",
      "text": "\tヒントを見ると[~ 伏字に共通の文字を入れるみたい、この「共通」がキーなのかも]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774526388,
      "updated": 1774526419
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51fd4000000000063707d",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 問題番号が書いてあるのは、その問題と何かが共通ということ？使われる文字とか？] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774526420,
      "updated": 1774526446
    },
    {
      "id": "69c51f8c000000000063707a",
      "text": "\t下の白黒バーの意味は何？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774526348,
      "updated": 1774526566
    },
    {
      "id": "69c52065000000000063707e",
      "text": "\t[~ FINALの横は26個、問題も26個、26番の先頭が赤いのはQ26の出題と一致、23が2文字なのとも合致]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774526566,
      "updated": 1774530950
    },
    {
      "id": "69c5316100000000006e6cbf",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 26といえばアルファベット？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774530914,
      "updated": 1774532224
    },
    {
      "id": "69c5312a00000000006e6cbe",
      "text": "\t[~ Q09とQ13]が解けたよ！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774530859,
      "updated": 1774532215
    },
    {
      "id": "69c5367700000000006e6cc1",
      "text": "\t[~ 上記が解けたことによるヒントを埋めていったらQ26, Q19]も解けた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774532215,
      "updated": 1774539542
    },
    {
      "id": "69c5366e00000000006e6cc0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774532207,
      "updated": 1774532207
    }
  ]
}